room_title: Escape room "Dark Side of the Moon" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque

room_description: You and your team are a group of scientists working on Area 53, a top-secret government facility on our moon that is used to test dangerous new experiments. A hostile genetic experiment has just escaped in the Dark Sector, and now your team must find your way off the moon and fast, or be eaten alive. Does your team have the skills to make it out alive? You have one hour...
